00:00:36.231 --> 00:00:39.772
into a separate cell when
we split the cytoplasm

00:00:39.772 --> 00:00:40.608
right over here.

00:00:40.608 --> 00:00:44.280
We split or the cell as
it turns into to cells.

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:47.552
Well, let's see how all of this happens.

