And we can draw the blue chromosome.

00:02:11.501 --> 00:02:13.045
Once again, it's now
in the condensed form.

00:02:13.045 --> 00:02:15.541
That's one sister
chromatid right over there.

00:02:15.541 --> 00:02:18.745
That's another sister chromatid.

00:02:18.745 --> 00:02:21.564
They are connected at the centromere.

00:02:23.752 --> 00:02:27.263
So they're condensing now
