incredibly complex thing.

00:03:17.956 --> 00:03:20.678
It kind of knows what to do even though

00:03:20.678 --> 00:03:22.594
it has no intelligence here.

00:03:22.594 --> 00:03:23.801
And a lot of what I'm talking about,

00:03:23.801 --> 00:03:26.576
the general overview of the
process is well understood

00:03:26.576 --> 00:03:29.455
but scientists are still
understanding exactly

00:03:29.455 --> 00:03:32.438
how do the different things
happen when they should happen

00:03:32.438 --> 00:03:34.817
and by what mechanism and
what's actually happening.

00:03:34.817 --> 00:03:38.417
Sometimes, molecular or atomic basis.

00:03:38.417 --> 00:03:41.296
But anyway, this first phase of mitosis,

00:03:41.296 --> 00:03:43.560
